a page display, below the page image  \u2013 e.g. Image produced by the Library of Congress. For more information on current NDNP awardees, see <a href=\"https://www.loc.gov/ndnp/listawardees.html\">https://www.loc.gov/ndnp/listawardees.html</a>.</p>\n<p>For more information on Library of Congress policies and disclaimers regarding rights and reproductions, see <a href=\"https://www.loc.gov/homepage/legal.html\">https://www.loc.gov/homepage/legal.html</a></p>"], "score": 14.331948, "shard": "06", "shelf_id": "sn87093407, 1920-07-08, Edition 1", "site": ["chroniclingamerica"], "source_group": "ndnp/wa", "source_modified": "2000-01-01T12:00:00Z", "subject": ["washington (state)", "seattle (wash.)", "king", "united states", "washington", "seattle", "newspapers"], "subject_headings": ["Seattle (Wash.)--Newspapers", "Washington (State)--Seattle", "United States--Washington--King--Seattle"], "subjects": [{"king": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:king&fo=json"}, {"newspapers": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:newspapers&fo=json"}, {"seattle": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:seattle&fo=json"}, {"seattle (wash.)": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:seattle+%28wash.%29&fo=json"}, {"united states": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:united+states&fo=json"}, {"washington": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:washington&fo=json"}, {"washington (state)": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:washington+%28state%29&fo=json"}], "timestamp": "2024-04-26T13:38:23.063Z", "title": "The Seattle star (Seattle, Wash.), July 8, 1920", "type": ["issue"], "url": "https://www.loc.gov/item/sn87093407/1920-07-08/ed-1/"}, "locations": null, "method": "mets_filesec", "more_like_this": [{"access_restricted": false, "aka": ["http://www.loc.gov/item/sn87093407/", "http://lccn.loc.gov/sn87093407"], "batch": ["wa_alki_ver01"], "campaigns": [], "date": "1899", "description": ["Daily (except Sunday) Began in 1899. -v. 49, no. 144 (Aug. 13, 1947). Archived issues are